Revision history for Tree-File

0.113   2015-02-??
        - Added github repo to dist metadata
        - Added x_deprecated to dist metadata to tag dist as deprecated

0.112   2013-01-01
        Don't bother trying to install on Win32.  Locking times out, and nobody
        should be using this anyway.

        Please don't use this library.  It was a dumb idea.

0.111   2010-10-19
        add missing YAML prereq

0.110   2006-11-13
        packaging improvements: kwalitee, license, perl critic, code clarity

0.10    2005-07-28
        avoid importing more symbols
        ...but do use Carp where needed
        more explicit division of logic in write_file
        added TODO test for writing branches without touching parents
        better reporting on lock failure

0.09    2005-07-28 09:00
        First release, unleashed on an unsuspecting world.

